<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Welcome to Our Library</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
        }
      .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: auto;
            background-color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        h1 {
            color: #333;
            text-align: center;
        }
        p {
            text-align: center;
            color: #666;
        }
        footer {
            text-align: center;
            color: #999;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Welcome {{name}}</h1>
        <p>We're thrilled to have you join our community. We hope you'll find everything you need among our books to enjoy.</p>
        <p>To get started, simply visit our main page and select the book that interests you. It's that easy!</p>
        <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, we're here for you. Don't hesitate to reach out to us.</p>
        <footer>
            <p>With warm regards,</p>
            <p>The Team at {{libraryName}}</p>
        </footer>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
